          <p><italic>P</italic>-values of 35 pairs of SNPs between genes <italic>KCNK5</italic> and <italic>PRDM13</italic> for testing interaction</p>
        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="989tbl3"/>
      </table-wrap>
      <fig id="F3" position="float">
